tweet: My prayers are with the family of Rep. Jimmy Martin, representative of Alabama's State District 42. Jimmy truly cared for the people he served and took his public office seriously. He represented Clanton, Chilton Co, and all of District 42 very well and he will be missed. #AL06

This week, the Alabama House passed a bill that would make almost all abortions illegal in Alabama. Performing or attempting to perform an abortion would be made felony offenses and would be punishable by imprisonment and fines. #AL06 #alpolitics
